text: George Southcote (1572–1638), of Shillingford, Devon, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Plympton Erle in 1597. ==References== Category:1572 births Category:1638 deaths Category:English MPs 1597–1598 Category:Members of the Parliament of England for Plympton Erle George
